These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peach, plum, radish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, dahlia, lily, amaryllis
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, romance, animation, horror
4 different games are played: chess, backgammon, canasta, mah-jongg
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, vegafina, tiparillo, cain
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person playing chess##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 7. the person watching animation movies is between the chaman-smoker and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 8. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 9. the person playing chess is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
10. the chaman-smoker is between the person watching animation movies and the person eating radish##2
11. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
12. the person watching horror movies is the person who growsamaryllis##1
13. the person playing canasta is between the person playing backgammon and the person who growslily##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea        | coffee       | lemonade  | almond-milk |
| Food          | radish     | plum         | peach     | broccoli    |
| Flower         | dahlia  | zinnia      | lily   | amaryllis     |
| Movie-Genre           | romance | family | animation   | horror     |
| Game   | backgammon    | canasta         | chess | mah-jongg         |
| Cigar         | cain     | chaman     | vegafina  | tiparillo       |

