.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, march, january, september
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, daisy, iris, azalea
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, analyst, manager, engineer
There 4 different types of food: peach, pepper, eggplant, garlic
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, german, malaysian, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, ship, train
 1. the german is between the person who growsiris and the person driving the bike##2
 2. the pakistani is on the left of the manager##1
 3. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the canadian##1
 4. the german is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person driving the ship##2
 5. the person eating peach is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 6. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1
 7. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the pilot and the person who growsazalea##2
 9. the analyst is the person who growsazalea##1
10. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1
11. the person eating peach is the manager##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
13. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
14. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Birthday      | september    | march       | january   | february |
| Flower         | daffodil     | iris   | azalea    | daisy  |
| Job   | pilot    | manager | analyst   | engineer     |
| Food   | garlic    | peach       | pepper | eggplant        |
| Nationality   | pakistani | malaysian   | german     | canadian    |
| Transport     | bus       | ship        | train      | bike        |

