The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, weightlifting, basketball, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, ship, tram, helicopter
 1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
