 4. the person traveling to london is on the left of the musician##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is between the analyst and the person eating zucchini##2
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is the person eating blueberry##1
10. the firefighter is the person driving the helicopter##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
